title: The Rebel Archetype Challenging Norms and Inspiring Change in AI
description: Exploring the Rebel archetype through myth and its potential application in AI development.
series: Archetypical
essay_number: 10
tags:
  - Archetypes
  - AI
  - Mythology
  - Rebel
